  m_text: 'In case of a Prestige reset, the game will restart. All <sprite name="chips">,
    <sprite name="token">, upgrades, Agents, and Modifiers will be lost.


    However,
    existing insights and purchased research will remain, which will make further
    resets progressively more valuable.


    It is recommended to use PPO in Normal
    Mode before resetting to gain <sprite name="insight"> multiplier.'
